<figureCitation id="1335F2DFFFB3C0548714FBF9BE38FBC8" box="[271,343,1054,1078]" captionStart="FIGURES 11 – 18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1916,1939]" captionTargetBox="[240,1346,465,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[228,1360,456,1907]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 11 – 18. Nicolaus abuensis sp. nov.: 11 &amp; 12. Head and thorax, female and male, respectively; 13. Male genital capsule, lateral view; 14. Mesal lobe of pygofer; 15. Connective, style, valve and subgenital plate, dorsal view; 16. Forewing; 17. Aedeagus, lateral view; 18. Aedeagus, dorsoanterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/228654/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">11–18</figureCitation>
