)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB1EE5AFFB3C054868CFB84BB2CFB60" blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Creamy white. Crown of head with submarginal brown stripe anteriorly. Face with arcuate lateral transverse stripes connected to median vertical stripe, brown; tiny spot on gena adjacent lorum, black.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB1EE5AFFB3C05486DCFB40BE64FB1D" blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Head shorter than median length of pronotum. Pronotum shorter than combined median length of scutum and scutellum.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C314BDD1FFB3C05486DCFB0ABE72F9E5" pageId="2" pageNumber="530" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BB1EE5AFFB3C05486DCFB0ABC33FA90" blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">
<emphasis id="B97A3248FFB3C05486DCFB0ABE18FAFB" box="[199,375,1261,1285]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Pygofer lobe caudally rounded, with three denticles along mesal margin. Subgenital plate notched near caudal tip on lateral margin and with sclerotized pad dorsally. Apophysis of style curved laterally, its mesal margin strongly crenulate, pigmented. Aedeagus with shaft membranous, preatrial processes bladelike, slightly bent dorsally at midlength and distally curved laterally.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB1EE5AFFB3C05486DCFA9FBC3AFA28" blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">
<emphasis id="B97A3248FFB3C05486DCFA9FBEFFFA6E" box="[199,400,1400,1424]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Female genitalia.</emphasis>
<collectingCountry id="F319AECAFFB3C0548783FA90BEBFFA6E" box="[408,464,1399,1424]" name="India" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Hind</collectingCountry>
margin of seventh sternite almost straight, with median narrowly V-shaped incision. First pair of valvulae abruptly narrowed before apex. Teeth on the second pair of valvulae in distal half close together, distance between them less than length of each tooth.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB1EE5AFFB3C05486DCFA06BE72F9E5" blockId="2.[151,1437,1122,1736]" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">
<emphasis id="B97A3248FFB3C05486DCFA06BE1EFA06" box="[199,369,1505,1528]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="530">Measurements.</emphasis>
